 *
 * Usage:
 *   instrument-runner --instrument-name <name> [--instrument-version <v>] \
 *     --param key=value --output-dir <path> [--dry-run]
 *
 *   instrument-runner --instrument <path-to-version-dir> \
 *     --param key=value --output-dir <path> [--dry-run]
 *
 * Instrument resolution (in priority order):
